data.description: Beautiful two story home surrounded by trees in the heart of The Woodlands. This home has a great layout with abundant natural light, and a spacious family room with a floor-to-ceiling brick fireplace. The updated kitchen features stainless steel appliances, a breakfast room with a bay window that opens to the family room. Three bedrooms along with the large primary bedroom can be found upstairs. A 5th bedroom with an attached full bathroom is located on the first floor. The backyard is fully fenced with plenty of shade to enjoy the flagstone patio.  Ideally located in a desired community with easy access to I-45, restaurants & shopping - THIS IS A MUST SEE- Schedule your showing today!
